WEBVTT

00:08.259 --> 00:10.845
- YOU WANNA KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
ON SHAMELESS  LAST YEAR?

00:10.845 --> 00:12.263
BROTHERS...
- DOCTORS.

00:12.263 --> 00:14.014
- I CAME OUT.
- HE CAME OUT!

00:14.014 --> 00:15.307
[overlapping chatter]

00:15.307 --> 00:18.186
- FIONA!
HE'S NOT BREATHING!

00:18.186 --> 00:20.063
- OH, MY GOD.
HE GOT INTO MY COKE.

00:20.063 --> 00:22.107
- FIONA GALLAGHER, YOU
HAVE THE RIGHT TO REMAIN SILENT.

00:22.107 --> 00:23.399
- I'M NOT GUILTY!

00:23.399 --> 00:24.775
- LIAM ALMOST DIED!

00:24.775 --> 00:26.444
- HOW DO YOU PLEAD?
- I'M GUILTY.

00:26.444 --> 00:29.114
- YOU WILL BE UNDER HOUSE ARREST
UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE.

00:29.114 --> 00:30.614
[beeping]

00:30.614 --> 00:32.074
- MY LIVER'S
FINALLY GIVING UP.

00:32.074 --> 00:33.993
- WANT ME TO STEAL YOU ONE
FROM THE GROCERY STORE?

00:33.993 --> 00:35.286
- NOT READY TO PUNCH
MY TICKET YET.

00:35.286 --> 00:36.787
- WE'RE NOT A MATCH.

00:36.787 --> 00:39.457
- EVEN MY OWN DAUGHTER
ISN'T A MATCH.

00:39.457 --> 00:41.459
- DAUGHTER?

00:41.459 --> 00:43.919
- THIS IS AMY,
AND THAT'S GEMMA.

00:43.919 --> 00:45.212
THE NURSES
JUST LEFT ME LIKE

00:45.212 --> 00:47.798
WE KNOW WHAT THE FUCK
WE'RE DOING.

00:47.798 --> 00:49.467
- I'M NOT A LITTLE GIRL.

00:49.467 --> 00:50.593
I'M READY.

00:50.593 --> 00:52.303
DOES THIS MAKE YOU CRAY?

00:52.303 --> 00:55.306
- UH--YOU'RE TOO YOUNG.
- OH, MY GOD.

00:55.306 --> 00:57.391
WHERE THE HELL WERE YOU?
- THE ARMY.

00:57.391 --> 00:58.517
- WHY'D YOU EVEN GO THERE
IN THE FIRST PLACE?

00:58.517 --> 01:00.186
- RELATIONSHIP ISSUES.

01:00.186 --> 01:01.479
- YOU'RE SICK OF LIVING A LIE,
AREN'T YOU?

01:01.479 --> 01:03.105
- I JUST WANT
EVERYBODY HERE TO KNOW

01:03.105 --> 01:05.524
I'M FUCKING GAY.

01:05.524 --> 01:07.818
YOU HAPPY NOW?

01:07.818 --> 01:09.862
- COLLEGE IS A LOT
FUCKING HARDER THAN IT LOOKS.

01:09.862 --> 01:12.072
YOU ACTUALLY HAVE TO APPLY
YOURSELF.

01:12.072 --> 01:13.324
- WHO EXACTLY IS AMANDA?

01:13.324 --> 01:15.201
- MY ROOMMATE'S
EX-GIRLFRIEND

01:15.201 --> 01:16.327
WHO TRIED TO BLOW ME
IN MY SLEEP.

01:16.327 --> 01:17.828
SHE BUYS ME SHIT.

01:17.828 --> 01:19.079
- SOUNDS LIKE A KEEPER.

01:19.079 --> 01:20.456
- NO MORE BULLSHIT
ABOUT BABY.

01:20.456 --> 01:21.749
YOU HELP.

01:21.749 --> 01:23.000
- YO, IT'S AFTER 5:00.

01:23.000 --> 01:24.376
HOW CAN YOU--
- JESUS, LEAVE ME ALONE!

01:24.376 --> 01:26.212
- IT COULD BE BIPOLAR DISEASE
LIKE OUR MOM.

01:26.212 --> 01:27.838
HE MAY HAVE
TO BE HOSPITALIZED.

01:27.838 --> 01:30.216
- NO FUCKING WAY!
HE'S STAYING WITH ME.

01:30.216 --> 01:32.551
- FIONA NEVER CAME HOME.
SHE VIOLATED PROBATION.

01:32.551 --> 01:33.636
- I FUCKED UP.

01:35.721 --> 01:39.058
- IT IS MY HONOR
TO DECLARE YOU MAN AND WIFE.

01:39.058 --> 01:41.269
- I NEED EVERYBODY TO MOVE!
- IS HE DEAD?

01:41.269 --> 01:43.229
- HE'S GETTING A LIVER.
- MRS. GALLAGHER?

01:43.229 --> 01:45.314
WE'RE MARRIED?
- LET ME SEE MY FATHER,

01:45.314 --> 01:46.941
YOU BITCH.
- NO!

01:46.941 --> 01:48.567
- YOU'RE CAMPING
IN MY YARD?

01:48.567 --> 01:50.569
- THE VACANT LOT
NEXT TO YOUR YARD.

01:50.569 --> 01:52.404
- GET YOUR STUFF.
YOU'RE OUT.

01:52.404 --> 01:55.200
- 20, 30--CAN'T BE ABOUT HOW
MUCH THEY SCREWED US UP ANYMORE.

01:55.200 --> 01:56.450
- SOUNDS KIND OF LIKE A.A.

01:56.450 --> 01:58.327
- ATTENDANCE IS A CONDITION
OF MY PAROLE.

01:58.327 --> 02:01.206
- COME ON, LET'S GO.
YOU GONNA BE LATE FOR WORK.

02:01.206 --> 02:02.665
- THANKS.

02:02.665 --> 02:03.791
- ARE YOU GONNA GO INSIDE?

02:03.791 --> 02:05.668
- NO.

02:05.668 --> 02:09.046
- I'M ALIVE, MOTHERFUCKER!

02:16.804 --> 02:19.807
[High Strung's
The Luck You Got  playing]

02:19.807 --> 02:23.561
♪ ♪

02:23.561 --> 02:27.106
- ♪ THINK OF ALL THE LUCK
YOU GOT ♪

02:27.106 --> 02:30.067
♪ KNOW THAT
IT'S NOT FOR NAUGHT ♪

02:30.067 --> 02:33.195
♪ YOU WERE BEAMING
ONCE BEFORE ♪

02:33.195 --> 02:37.491
♪ BUT IT'S NOT LIKE THAT
ANYMORE ♪

02:37.491 --> 02:41.036
♪ WHAT IS THIS DOWNSIDE ♪

02:41.036 --> 02:44.331
♪ THAT YOU SPEAK OF? ♪

02:44.331 --> 02:46.625
♪ WHAT IS THIS FEELING ♪

02:46.625 --> 02:51.381
♪ YOU'RE SO SURE OF? ♪

02:51.381 --> 02:58.304
♪ ♪

02:58.304 --> 03:01.181
♪ ROUND UP THE FRIENDS
YOU GOT ♪

03:01.181 --> 03:04.393
♪ KNOW THAT
THEY'RE NOT FOR NAUGHT ♪

03:04.393 --> 03:07.771
♪ YOU WERE WILLING
ONCE BEFORE ♪

03:07.771 --> 03:12.109
♪ BUT IT'S NOT LIKE THAT
ANYMORE ♪

03:12.109 --> 03:15.362
♪ WHAT IS THIS DOWNSIDE ♪

03:15.362 --> 03:19.242
♪ THAT YOU SPEAK OF? ♪

03:19.242 --> 03:21.118
♪ WHAT IS THIS FEELING ♪

03:21.118 --> 03:24.246
♪ YOU'RE SO SURE OF ♪

03:25.914 --> 03:27.583
[Christian & the 2120s'
Smile At Trouble  playing]

03:27.583 --> 03:35.674
♪ ♪

04:03.952 --> 04:06.331
- SHEILS.
- HMM?

04:06.331 --> 04:09.249
- WHAT'S HE DOING
IN OUR BED?

04:09.249 --> 04:10.542
- WHO?

04:13.212 --> 04:16.507
- HIM. HIS PECKER'S POKING ME
IN THE BACK.

04:16.507 --> 04:21.387
- OH, SAMMI PICKED UP SOME GUY
AT THE ALIBI LAST NIGHT

04:21.387 --> 04:24.264
AND KICKED CHUCKIE
OUT OF HER TRAILER.

04:24.264 --> 04:25.516
- KAREN'S ROOM?

04:25.516 --> 04:27.352
- I TUCKED HIM IN THERE.

04:27.352 --> 04:29.645
HE MUST'VE CRAWLED IN
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

04:29.645 --> 04:31.439
- WELL, HE'S GOT TO UNCRAWL.

04:31.439 --> 04:32.981
[grunts]
[thud]

04:32.981 --> 04:35.067
- OW.

04:35.067 --> 04:38.862
- OH, CHUCKIE, WHY DIDN'T YOU
STAY IN KAREN'S ROOM?

04:38.862 --> 04:40.447
- I HAD A BAD DREAM.

04:40.447 --> 04:44.243
- WELL, YOU MIGHT AS WELL GET UP
AND GET READY FOR SCHOOL.

04:44.243 --> 04:47.330
AND YOU MISTER,
MEDS AND VITALS.

04:47.330 --> 04:48.288
- CAN'T.

04:48.288 --> 04:50.290
GOT TO WORK ON MY PROJECT.
BUSY.

04:50.290 --> 04:54.128
- FRANK,
MEDS AND VITALS NOW!

04:54.128 --> 04:57.005
[rock music]

04:57.005 --> 05:04.304
♪ ♪

05:04.304 --> 05:09.893
[cheers and applause]

05:09.893 --> 05:11.354
- WHY THEY TEARING IT DOWN?

05:11.354 --> 05:13.021
- ASBESTOS.

05:14.357 --> 05:18.026
[cheers and applause]

05:18.026 --> 05:20.112
- ALL RIGHT, I'M LEAVING.
I'VE SEEN ENOUGH.

05:20.112 --> 05:22.698
- WAIT, GIVE ME A RIDE HOME
ON THE BACK OF THAT THING.

05:22.698 --> 05:24.700
- CAN'T. GOT TO RUN AN ERRAND
THEN GOING TO SCHOOL.

05:24.700 --> 05:26.744
- I'M NOT.
- IT'S THE LAST DAY.

05:26.744 --> 05:28.454
YOU HAVE TO GO.
- WHY,

05:28.454 --> 05:30.415
SO I CAN FIGURE OUT HOW
TO FLUNK SIXTH GRADE AGAIN?

05:30.415 --> 05:31.707
YEAH, I'LL DO THAT
NEXT YEAR.

05:31.707 --> 05:33.500
COME ON,
JUST GIVE ME A RIDE.

05:33.500 --> 05:35.502
- YOU CAN'T EVEN FIT ON MY BIKE
WITH THAT GIANT GIMP LEG.

05:35.502 --> 05:36.879
- THESE CRUTCHES
ARE KILLING MY WRISTS.

05:36.879 --> 05:38.589
I CAN'T EVEN JACK OFF
THAT WELL.

05:38.589 --> 05:40.466
- SHOULD'VE THOUGHT ABOUT THAT
BEFORE YOU BUSTED UP

05:40.466 --> 05:42.552
YOUR ANKLE
ON YOUR STUPID SKATEBOARD.

05:42.552 --> 05:43.886
SEE YOU.

05:49.349 --> 05:51.394
- LOOKS PRETTY GOOD, HUH?

05:51.394 --> 05:55.314
- IT'S PERFECT...
EXCEPT FOR ONE THING.

05:55.314 --> 05:56.523
- WHAT?

05:56.523 --> 05:59.359
- UH-OH.
- MM-HMM.

05:59.359 --> 06:00.360
- LOOKS LIKE
WE'RE STUCK IN HERE

06:00.360 --> 06:01.737
FOREVER.
- YEP.

06:01.737 --> 06:03.697
- I GUESS WE--WE TRAPPED?

06:03.697 --> 06:05.157
- YEAH.
- NO WAY OUT.

06:05.157 --> 06:06.576
- THAT'S RIGHT,
WE'RE TRAPPED.

06:06.576 --> 06:07.367
- YOU'RE NEVER GONNA
SEE ANY ONE OF

06:07.367 --> 06:09.536
PATSY'S PIES EVER AGAIN.

06:09.536 --> 06:10.704
- OH, LIAM,

06:10.704 --> 06:12.706
THIS IS OUR NEW HOME NOW.
- OKAY.

06:12.706 --> 06:13.957
- [laughing]

06:13.957 --> 06:16.835
[mellow rock music]

06:16.835 --> 06:24.885
♪ ♪

06:27.805 --> 06:29.181
- I'M GONNA GET THE LADDER.

06:29.181 --> 06:32.602
- MM-HMM.
DON'T TWIST AN ANKLE.

06:32.602 --> 06:34.561
- PLEASE.

06:34.561 --> 06:36.522
DON'T WORRY.

06:36.522 --> 06:38.524
AH!
- [laughing]

06:38.524 --> 06:40.359
- [screaming]

06:40.359 --> 06:42.903
- IMPRESSIVE.
- THANK YOU.

06:42.903 --> 06:44.738
THANK YOU.

06:44.738 --> 06:47.032
- YOU READY TO FILL
THIS SUCKER, LIAM?

06:47.032 --> 06:48.576
- YEAH!

06:48.576 --> 06:50.702
- RIGHT ON, HERE YOU GO.
- YEP.

06:50.702 --> 06:54.081
- ALL RIGHT, ATTACH THIS END
TO THE FIRE HYDRANT.

06:54.081 --> 06:56.750
- HOW ARE WE GONNA
OPEN THE VALVE?

06:56.750 --> 06:58.836
- GALLAGHER INGENUITY.

06:58.836 --> 07:00.587
- YOU GOT ONE
OF THOSE LYING AROUND?

07:00.587 --> 07:02.422
- YOU DON'T?

07:02.422 --> 07:04.842
COME ON.

07:04.842 --> 07:06.677
- ALL RIGHT.
HERE, STEP ASIDE.

07:06.677 --> 07:07.970
THIS GOES HERE.

07:07.970 --> 07:09.597
YOU WANT TO HELP?
- MM-HMM.

07:09.597 --> 07:11.598
- OKAY,
WATCH YOUR FINGERS.

07:14.059 --> 07:16.436
HERE IT COMES.

07:16.436 --> 07:17.605
- OOH.

07:19.189 --> 07:21.984
[laughing]
- [screaming]

07:21.984 --> 07:25.237
- NO, NO, NOW, COME ON.
I'M YOUR FUCKING BOSS.

07:25.237 --> 07:26.822
- UH-HUH.
- OH, NO, NO.

07:26.822 --> 07:28.699
I MAY NOT
HAVE HIRED YOU,

07:28.699 --> 07:29.741
BUT I SURE AS HELL
CAN FIRE YOU.

07:29.741 --> 07:31.034
- NO, NO, NO.
- YES.

07:31.034 --> 07:32.828
- [screaming]
- [laughing]

07:32.828 --> 07:34.496
- HOLD IT--GIVE ME THAT.
GIVE ME THAT.

07:34.496 --> 07:36.081
- NO, NO.
[screaming]

07:36.081 --> 07:40.586
- SEAN, NO, NO.
AH! OH, MY GOD.

07:40.586 --> 07:42.588
OH, MY GOD.
I'M GONNA HURT YOU.

07:42.588 --> 07:46.466
- [screaming]
- BOOM! BOOM, I SAY, BOOM!

07:46.466 --> 07:49.386
HOW DID YOU GET SO WET?
[Liam screeching]

07:49.386 --> 07:50.721
- DON'T YOU GOT TO GO?
- I DO.

07:50.721 --> 07:53.098
IN FACT, I GOT TO GO
TAKE MY SON TO SCHOOL.

07:53.098 --> 07:55.017
COME ON,
I GOT TO GET WILL.

07:55.017 --> 07:56.602
- ALL RIGHT,
TELL HIM I SAY "HI."

07:56.602 --> 07:58.061
- I WILL, I WILL.
I'LL SEE YOU FOR DINNER.

07:58.061 --> 07:59.396
- OKAY.
- ALL RIGHT.

07:59.396 --> 08:02.190
[rock music]

08:02.190 --> 08:07.779
♪ ♪

08:07.779 --> 08:12.660
[cheering]

08:12.660 --> 08:15.162
- WE GET IT, MORONS.
SCHOOL'S OUT.

08:16.997 --> 08:20.375
- YOU'RE NOT EVEN PACKED?
- YOU LOOK CUTE.

08:20.375 --> 08:22.586
- IT'S SUMMER.
YOU HAVE A SUITCASE?

08:22.586 --> 08:24.838
- IT'S RIGHT THERE.
- LOUIS VUITTON?

08:24.838 --> 08:27.799
- NO, IT'S A GUCCI.
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

08:27.799 --> 08:31.219
- I'M FILLING OUT AN APPLICATION
TO BE AN R.A. IN THE FALL.

08:31.219 --> 08:32.680
- REALLY?
- "RESIDENT ASSHOLE."

08:32.680 --> 08:36.266
[laughter]
- WHY NOT, YOU KNOW?

08:36.266 --> 08:38.644
IT'S FREE ROOM AND BOARD,
ALL THE BEER I CAN CONFISCATE.

08:38.644 --> 08:41.229
- WELL, YOU COULD JUST STAY WITH
ME AT MY OFF-CAMPUS APARTMENT.

08:41.229 --> 08:44.066
MY DAD'S PAYING.
THAT MAKES IT FREE.

08:44.066 --> 08:45.735
- YOU MEAN, LIKE,
LIVE TOGETHER?

08:45.735 --> 08:47.319
- WELL, ISN'T THAT
WHAT WE'VE BEEN DOING

08:47.319 --> 08:48.695
FOR THE LAST FOUR MONTHS?

08:48.695 --> 08:50.989
- YEAH, BUT YOU GOT
YOUR OWN DORM ROOM.

08:50.989 --> 08:52.532
- I'M GONNA MISS MY PLANE.

08:55.118 --> 08:57.329
- LOOK, HAVE A GOOD SUMMER,
MAN, YEAH?

08:57.329 --> 08:58.705
- YOU TOO, DUDE.

08:58.705 --> 09:00.332
- IT'S BEEN REAL.

09:00.332 --> 09:03.126
- LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

09:03.126 --> 09:06.546
- IT'S THE ONLY ONE I COULD FIND
IN ALL THE CRAP OUT IN THE YARD.

09:06.546 --> 09:08.048
- PUT IT IN THE WINDOW.

09:08.048 --> 09:10.384
YOU WANT SCRAMBLED
OR FRIED?

09:10.384 --> 09:12.552
- I LIKE THOSE PUFFY EGGS
YOU MAKE.

09:12.552 --> 09:15.514
- NIKA,
WE GOT BAKED EGGS TODAY.

09:15.514 --> 09:16.724
- FOOD IS FOOD.

09:16.724 --> 09:18.058
[baby cries]
ALL THE SAME TO ME.

09:18.058 --> 09:19.601
- WHY'S THE BABY CRYING?

09:19.601 --> 09:21.144
- LOOK AT YOU.

09:22.562 --> 09:24.564
- OOH, DIAPER FULL OF POOP.

09:24.564 --> 09:26.608
[gasps] DA?
- OH...

09:26.608 --> 09:28.736
IS THAT WHAT HAPPENED?
- [speaking Russian]

09:28.736 --> 09:30.028
- DON'T WANT HIM COVERED
IN BABY SHIT

09:30.028 --> 09:33.490
ON HIS FIRST DAY OF WORK.

09:33.490 --> 09:35.575
- WE HAVE BAKED EGGS
IN THE OVEN.

09:35.575 --> 09:38.746
- HEY, MORON, TRUCK READY?
- YEAH.

09:38.746 --> 09:41.415
- YOU STARE ANY LONGER,
I CHOP YOUR DICKS OFF.

09:41.415 --> 09:43.750
- TIME TO GO PLAY NICEY-NICE
WITH SURROGATES,

09:43.750 --> 09:45.794
MEET THEM
AT THE ULTRASOUND.

09:45.794 --> 09:47.755
- THEY STILL THINK
YOU'RE A KINDERGARTEN TEACHER?

09:47.755 --> 09:49.631
- WHEELS ON THE BUS
GO ROUND AND ROUND.

09:49.631 --> 09:51.883
- AMAZING WHAT PEOPLE
WITH MONEY WILL PAY FOR.

09:51.883 --> 09:54.219
- AFTER ULTRASOUND,
I GO OPEN RUB 'N TUG.

09:54.219 --> 09:56.596
YOU FEED YEV BREAKFAST,
AND YOU GO TO GROCERY STORE.

09:56.596 --> 09:58.056
- GOT IT.

09:58.056 --> 09:59.933
- HEY, PATEL HIT
ONE OF THE GIRLS YESTERDAY,

09:59.933 --> 10:01.101
LEFT WITHOUT PAY.

10:01.101 --> 10:03.562
- DRY CLEANER PATEL?
- UH-HUH.

10:03.562 --> 10:04.730
- I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.

10:04.730 --> 10:06.231
LET'S GO.

10:06.231 --> 10:07.899
NO, NO, NO, GUNS.

10:07.899 --> 10:10.110
LOOK, NO HARDWARE.

10:10.110 --> 10:11.821
IT'S NOT THAT KIND OF JOB.

10:11.821 --> 10:15.658
WE'RE RESPECTABLE NOW,
REMEMBER?

10:15.658 --> 10:16.950
- DO YOU WANT THIS?

10:16.950 --> 10:18.577
- I'LL MEET YOU AT THE PLACE
LATER, OKAY?

10:21.913 --> 10:24.124
- I'LL BE THERE.

10:24.124 --> 10:25.710
- BETTER BE.

10:30.672 --> 10:32.632
- MM.

10:32.632 --> 10:34.468
WHAT THE HELL?
I'M IN HERE.

10:34.468 --> 10:36.845
- GOTTA PEE BAD.

10:36.845 --> 10:40.725
- WHAT'S THE POINT?
NOTHING'S HAPPENING ANYWAY.

10:40.725 --> 10:43.226
- ARE YOU TAKING
YOUR MEDICATIONS?

10:43.226 --> 10:44.770
- YES!

10:44.770 --> 10:49.191
[Chuckie urinating]

10:49.191 --> 10:50.735
- WHAT ARE THOSE FOR?

10:50.735 --> 10:53.445
- ANTI-REJECTION,
ULCERS,

10:53.445 --> 10:56.031
HYPERTENSION,
HIGH BLOOD PRESSURE,

10:56.031 --> 10:58.743
DEPRESSION, HEADACHES,
DIURETIC,

10:58.743 --> 11:02.204
AND APPARENTLY I NEED ONE
FOR CONSTIPATION NOW TOO.

11:06.124 --> 11:07.292
A LOT OF PEE.

11:07.292 --> 11:08.543
- HELD IT ALL NIGHT.

11:08.543 --> 11:09.753
- ARE YOU WEIGHING
YOURSELF?

11:09.753 --> 11:11.797
I DON'T HEAR THE SCALE.

11:15.467 --> 11:19.012
I HEAR THE SCALE NOW.

11:21.306 --> 11:22.725
- 155.

11:22.725 --> 11:25.143
- IT SAYS 147.

11:25.143 --> 11:26.812
- 155.

11:26.812 --> 11:29.689
- YOU LIE TO YOUR NOTEBOOK?
- YOUR GRANDMOTHER

11:29.689 --> 11:31.066
DOESN'T NEED TO KNOW
I'VE LOST SOME WEIGHT.

11:31.066 --> 11:33.903
- BLOOD PRESSURE.
- OH, JESUS!

11:46.540 --> 11:48.834
- [crying]

11:48.834 --> 11:52.045
- OH, WHY CAN'T YOU GIRLS JUST
MAKE THIS EASY FOR ME JUST ONCE?

11:52.045 --> 11:53.421
- GIRL, HERE,
GIVE ME THAT THING.

11:53.421 --> 11:54.756
HERE.

11:56.967 --> 11:58.928
- MAMA, STOP.
I'M NOT A COW.

11:58.928 --> 12:00.470
- LOOK, YOU GOT
TO GRAB THIS TIT,

12:00.470 --> 12:01.763
AND YOU GOT TO MASSAGE IT

12:01.763 --> 12:03.933
TILL YOU GET THE MILK DUCTS
FLOWING, GIRL.

12:03.933 --> 12:05.892
- I KNOW HOW TO DO IT.
STOP.

12:05.892 --> 12:09.312
- HOW ARE MY FOUR FAVORITE
LADIES DOING AND MY LITTLE MAN?

12:09.312 --> 12:12.942
- WELL, I GOT THEM BIG,
BROWN FLYING SAUCERS WORKING.

12:12.942 --> 12:16.695
THAT'S RIGHT, DOMINICK,
OUR JOB HERE IS DONE.

12:16.695 --> 12:18.530
- BYE-BYE, D.
- SAY, "BYE-BYE."

12:18.530 --> 12:21.158
- BYE-BYE, D.

12:21.158 --> 12:23.743
- OW. AMY,
YOU BITING ME AGAIN.

12:23.743 --> 12:26.079
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
DO NOT HIT OUR DAUGHTER.

12:26.079 --> 12:28.206
IT'S JUST THE NIPPLE.
- JUST THE NIPPLE?

12:28.206 --> 12:29.541
LET'S SEE HOW YOU LIKE IT.

12:29.541 --> 12:31.835
- OW! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
- [crying]

12:31.835 --> 12:33.879
- NOW LOOK WHAT YOU DID.
- WHAT I DID?

12:33.879 --> 12:35.589
YOU'RE THE ONE TITTY TWISTING
AND MOVING HER ALL AROUND.

12:35.589 --> 12:37.174
- SHH.
- DON'T SHUSH ME.

12:37.174 --> 12:39.969
- YOUR TURN.
HI, GEMMA.

12:39.969 --> 12:42.137
HERE WE GO, BABY.

