TO CALL THAT DOCTOR?

19:21.286 --> 19:23.621
- WHICH ONE?
- FROM THE CLINIC.

19:23.621 --> 19:25.873
- NO, NO.
I'M GOOD.

19:25.873 --> 19:29.127
- WELL, PROBABLY THE BEST TIME
TO GO WHEN YOU'RE FEELING GOOD.

19:29.127 --> 19:31.296
- WHY IS THAT?
- JUST TO HAVE A PLAN OF ACTION

19:31.296 --> 19:33.339
