- ABSOLUTELY.

24:50.489 --> 24:52.074
HEY, TIE THOSE DOWN.

24:52.074 --> 24:53.200
WE DON'T WANT
THEM MOVING AROUND.

24:53.200 --> 24:56.078
[mellow rock music]

24:56.078 --> 25:03.210
♪ ♪

25:03.210 --> 25:05.630
BYE, LITTLE GUY.

25:05.630 --> 25:13.722
♪ ♪

25:15.181 --> 25:17.350
- DEBS, CARL,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

25:17.350 --> 25:18.768
- I HATE YOU STUPID BITCHES!

25:18.768 --> 25:20.686
- WELL, HOW WAS YOUR LAST DAY
OF SCHOOL, DEBS?

25:20.686 --> 25:22.188
IS THERE ANYTHING
YOU WANT TO

25:22.188 --> 25:23.607
TALK ABOUT?
- NO.

25:23.607 --> 25:26.192
- YO, FUCKWAD.

25:26.192 --> 25:27.652
- HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON,
STUMPY?

25:27.652 --> 25:29.570
- I GOT SOME NEW PIERCINGS.
- YEAH, I CAN SEE THAT.

25:29.570 --> 25:31.530
- AND I PICKED UP SOME HERB
FOR OUR GUYS.

25:31.530 --> 25:33.741
YOU WANT TO COME?
- EH...

25:33.741 --> 25:35.702
YEAH, SURE. LOOK,

25:35.702 --> 25:38.663
I'M JUST GONNA BE OVER THERE
IF YOU NEED ANYTHING, OKAY?

25:38.663 --> 25:40.373
- LOOK WHO I FOUND
TROLLING THE STREETS.

25:40.373 --> 25:41.625
- YO.

25:41.625 --> 25:43.167
- THERE HE IS.
- OH, THERE HE IS.

25:43.167 --> 25:45.962
- LIP, HEARD YOU BEEN
UP AT COLLEGE OR SOME SHIT?

25:45.962 --> 25:48.255
- YEAH, YEAH.
I'VE BEEN OVER THERE A WHILE.

25:48.255 --> 25:49.715
WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH YOU GUYS?

25:49.715 --> 25:51.926
- SHIT. SAME OLD CRAP.
- YEAH.

25:51.926 --> 25:54.136
DID YOU BANG A BUNCH
OF COEDS UP AT SCHOOL?

25:54.136 --> 25:55.554
- YEAH, SURE.

25:55.554 --> 25:58.015
HEY, YOU STILL
AT YOUR DAD'S CHOP SHOP, WAYNE?

25:58.015 --> 25:59.601
- AH, WHEN HE GETS THE WORK.

25:59.601 --> 26:00.935
TOWELHEADS ARE GETTING MOST
OF THE SCRAP NOW.

26:00.935 --> 26:04.648
STUMPY KNOCKED UP GLORIA HU.
- OH, SHIT.

26:04.648 --> 26:06.650
- SHE SQUIRTED A KID OUT,
LIKE, TWO MONTHS AGO.

26:06.650 --> 26:08.526
I AIN'T CONVINCED
IT'S MINE THOUGH.

26:08.526 --> 26:10.569
I'M SAVING UP
TO GET ONE OF THOSE DNA TESTS.

26:10.569 --> 26:11.862
- RIGHT.

26:11.862 --> 26:13.781
- LOOK AT THAT FANCY WATCH.
- OOH.

26:13.781 --> 26:16.200
- THEY GIVING THOSE OUT
UP AT COLLEGE?

26:16.200 --> 26:18.536
- NO, I SWIPED IT
FROM A KID'S DORM ROOM.

26:18.536 --> 26:20.789
IT'S THE RICH PRICK'S FAULT
FOR LEAVING HIS DOOR UNLOCKED.

26:20.789 --> 26:22.624
- OH, LOOK AT THIS
PRETTY LADY,

26:22.624 --> 26:24.291
SOME DUST MY UNCLE
SCORED FOR ME.

26:24.291 --> 26:25.459
- FUCKING PUT THAT SHIT
ON THE WEED.

26:25.459 --> 26:27.336
- HOLDING OUT ON US.

26:27.336 --> 26:28.796
- YO, GUYS,
I GOT TO SPLIT, ALL RIGHT?

26:28.796 --> 26:30.799
- NO, NO, COME ON.
- HEY, IT'S GOOD SHIT,

26:30.799 --> 26:32.383
DID SOME LAST NIGHT
AT LAUREN CHAMBERS' PARTY.

26:32.383 --> 26:34.427
- NO, I'LL HANG LATER.
I HAVEN'T BEEN HOME YET.

26:34.427 --> 26:36.638
- ALL RIGHT, PUSSY,
SEE YOU LATER.

26:36.638 --> 26:39.098
- HOOK THAT SHIT UP,
STUMP.

26:42.727 --> 26:45.229
- HERE'S YOUR CHECK.

26:45.229 --> 26:48.816
BE RIGHT BACK
TO TAKE YOUR ORDER.

26:48.816 --> 26:50.776
GONNA HAVE YOUR FOOD
RIGHT OUT.

26:50.776 --> 26:52.153
HEY, ANGELA.

26:52.153 --> 26:54.113
- HI, FIONA.
- YOU KNOW WHAT YOU WANT?

26:54.113 --> 26:56.240
- I DO.

26:56.240 --> 26:58.200
I'LL TAKE THE BLUEBERRY PIE
THIS TIME.

26:58.200 --> 26:59.618
- YOU GOT IT.
CUP OF COFFEE?

26:59.618 --> 27:01.412
- YEP.
HOW'S LIFE?

27:01.412 --> 27:02.747
BEEN SEEING ANYBODY?

27:02.747 --> 27:04.457
- NAH.
I'M BORING THESE DAYS.

27:04.457 --> 27:06.500
- DOUBT THAT.
- [laughs]

27:06.500 --> 27:08.794
POLO, CAN YOU GET ANGELA
A CUP OF COFFEE

27:08.794 --> 27:10.921
AND A SLICE OF BLUEBERRY?
- YES, MISS FIONA.

27:10.921 --> 27:12.923
- ADAM,
I SWEAR I ORDERED IT.

27:12.923 --> 27:15.134
IT'S ON THE CHECK,
CHICKEN PARMESAN.

27:15.134 --> 27:16.677
NO, COME ON.
THE CUSTOMER'S ALREADY

27:16.677 --> 27:17.970
SO PISSED AT ME.
WHAT IS GOING ON?

27:17.970 --> 27:19.305
- HERE,
HAVE MY CHICKEN PARM.

27:19.305 --> 27:20.598
CAN YOU MAKE ANOTHER ONE
FAST, PLEASE?

27:20.598 --> 27:22.308
- THANK YOU, THANK YOU,
THANK YOU.

27:22.308 --> 27:23.768
- THAT ORIENTAL CHICK,
ANGELA,

27:23.768 --> 27:25.687
JUST ASKED ME
HOW MUCH YOU MAKE HERE.

27:25.687 --> 27:27.271
- I DON'T KNOW WHAT HER DEAL IS.
- I DO.

27:27.271 --> 27:29.899
SHE WANTS SOME FIONA PIE.

27:29.899 --> 27:31.484
- IS EVERYBODY OKAY?

27:31.484 --> 27:34.487
- WANDA'S
SEXUALLY HARASSING ME.

27:34.487 --> 27:35.988
- WELL,
I'LL SPANK HER LATER.

27:35.988 --> 27:38.783
- HER?
WHAT ABOUT ME?

27:38.783 --> 27:40.409
- UH, THE GUYS FROM JEZEBEL
JUST CAME IN.

27:40.409 --> 27:42.787
THEY ASKED FOR YOU. TABLE 13.
- OH, GOODIE.

27:42.787 --> 27:46.207
WELL, IF YOU WON'T SPANK ME,
MAYBE THEIR LEAD SINGER WILL.

27:49.418 --> 27:51.837
HERE YOU GO,
CHEESEBURGER,

27:51.837 --> 27:54.006
SPAGHETTI AND MEATBALLS
FOR THE GENTLEMAN.

27:54.006 --> 27:55.508
I'LL GET YOU
ANOTHER ICED TEA.

27:55.508 --> 27:57.009
- OKAY, THANKS.

28:00.889 --> 28:02.556
- LEFT YOU A HUNDRED BUCKS
AGAIN?

28:02.556 --> 28:04.475
- YEAH.
- GOT TO SEND HER TO MY SECTION

28:04.475 --> 28:05.768
AT LEAST ONCE.

28:12.776 --> 28:14.778
- HI, GUYS.
- HEY.

28:14.778 --> 28:16.112
- HEY, FIONA.
- HEY, DARLING.

28:16.112 --> 28:17.863
- LEFTOVER PIE?
- THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

28:17.863 --> 28:19.198
- YOU ARE SO WELCOME.

28:20.449 --> 28:22.034
- CAN YOU STARE
A LITTLE HARDER?

28:22.034 --> 28:23.786
- GET BACK TO WORK.
- [scoffs]

28:25.579 --> 28:28.749
- HELLO?

28:28.749 --> 28:30.292
HELLO?

28:33.337 --> 28:34.839
HELLO?

28:36.132 --> 28:37.759
[sighs]

28:52.982 --> 28:54.150
[sniffs]

28:56.902 --> 28:58.112
[sniffs]

28:58.112 --> 29:02.366
OH, GOD DAMN IT!

29:02.366 --> 29:07.163
WHAT KIND OF A WOMAN HAS SEX
IN ANOTHER WOMAN'S LIVING ROOM?

29:07.163 --> 29:09.582
FOR GOD SAKES!

29:09.582 --> 29:12.459
[rock music]

29:12.459 --> 29:20.134
♪ ♪

29:20.134 --> 29:23.846
OH...NO...SHE...DIDN'T!

29:23.846 --> 29:27.141
- ♪ THE KING OF BABEL
TOOK A FALL ♪

29:27.141 --> 29:29.935
♪ WHILE HIS SUBJECTS
CLIMBED THE WALLS ♪

29:29.935 --> 29:32.563
♪ ALL HIS HORSES AND HIS MEN ♪

29:32.563 --> 29:34.690
- MY SEX TOYS?
AH!

29:34.690 --> 29:36.358
- ♪ COULDN'T PUT HIM
TOGETHER AGAIN ♪

29:36.358 --> 29:38.736
♪ I'M DAMAGED, DAMAGED
DAMAGED INTO ♪

29:38.736 --> 29:42.698
♪ DAMAGED, DAMAGED
DAMAGED INTO ♪

29:42.698 --> 29:45.784
♪ LOVE ♪

29:45.784 --> 29:52.666
♪ ♪

29:52.666 --> 29:54.627
[gasps]
FRANK!

29:56.086 --> 29:58.006
FRANK!
- I TOLD YOU,

29:58.006 --> 29:59.883
I'M NOT READY
TO SHARE MY PROJECT YET, SHEILS.

29:59.883 --> 30:01.800
- IT'S NOT
ABOUT YOUR PROJECT.

30:01.800 --> 30:04.386
IT'S ABOUT SAMMI.

30:04.386 --> 30:08.016
EVER SINCE YOU GOT BETTER,
SHE IS REALLY ACTING OUT.

30:08.016 --> 30:10.684
- A GROWN WOMAN
CAN DO WHAT SHE LIKES.

30:10.684 --> 30:13.062
- WELL, SHE HAS REAL ISSUES.

30:13.062 --> 30:14.855
I MEAN, IF YOU DON'T START
PLAYING DADDY,

30:14.855 --> 30:16.858
THINGS ARE ONLY
GONNA GET WORSE.

30:16.858 --> 30:18.817
- I'M BUSY.
GOT A LOT OF WORK.

30:18.817 --> 30:20.904
- WELL, FRANK,

30:20.904 --> 30:23.031
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA DO ANYTHING
ABOUT IT, THEN I DON'T WANT HER

30:23.031 --> 30:25.866
AND THAT CHUCKIE THING
IN MY HOUSE ANYMORE.

30:25.866 --> 30:27.701
- WELL, FINE.

30:27.701 --> 30:29.161
WHATEVER.

30:29.161 --> 30:30.746
- REALLY?
THAT'S IT?

30:30.746 --> 30:32.039
- SURE.

30:34.250 --> 30:35.834
WHAT DO I CARE?

30:35.834 --> 30:39.338
- OH, WELL, GOOD.
I'M GLAD WE HAD THIS TALK.

30:40.422 --> 30:43.342
[Muzak playing]

30:43.342 --> 30:50.849
♪ ♪

30:56.897 --> 30:57.982
- WHAT'S GOING ON, IAN?

30:57.982 --> 31:00.068
HOW YOU DOING?

31:00.068 --> 31:01.860
- HEY, KEV.
WHAT'S UP?

31:01.860 --> 31:04.321
- JUST LOOKING FOR SOMETHING
TO GET GEMMA TO GO POOP.

31:04.321 --> 31:05.907
OH, HEY, LIAM.

31:05.907 --> 31:08.492
HEY, YEV, UH,
WHATEVER YOUR NAME IS.

31:08.492 --> 31:10.411
YOU GOT ANY SUGGESTIONS?

31:10.411 --> 31:14.164
- PUREED PEARS AND GLYCERIN
SUPPOSITORY WORK FOR THIS GUY.

31:14.164 --> 31:15.207
DIAPER AISLE.

31:15.207 --> 31:17.043
- THANKS, MAN.

31:17.043 --> 31:19.128
HEY, LET ME ASK YOU SOMETHING.

31:19.128 --> 31:20.879
YOU STILL BREAST FEED?

31:20.879 --> 31:23.632
I MEAN, WELL, NOT YOU,
BUT I MEAN, YOU KNOW, SVETLANA.

31:23.632 --> 31:25.259
- YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.
SHE'S INTO IT.

31:25.259 --> 31:27.970
IT'S, UH, GOOD
FOR THE BABY'S IMMUNE SYSTEM.

31:27.970 --> 31:29.471
- I KNEW IT.

31:29.471 --> 31:30.889
- PLUS, IT'S FREE, RIGHT?

31:30.889 --> 31:33.309
- FORGOT THAT ARGUMENT.

31:34.643 --> 31:36.895
ARE YOU COOL WITH THIS DUDE
CRUISING YOU?

31:36.895 --> 31:38.605
- YEAH, I'M FINE WITH IT.

31:38.605 --> 31:40.733
- ALL RIGHT, WELL, LET ME KNOW
IF YOU WANT ME TO ROUGH HIM UP.

31:40.733 --> 31:42.067
- OKAY.

31:48.324 --> 31:51.201
[rock music]

31:51.201 --> 31:59.084
♪ ♪

32:18.479 --> 32:19.730
- ABOUT TIME.
- FUCK YOU.

32:19.730 --> 32:21.315
I DIDN'T KNOW
SHE HAD A PIANO.

32:21.315 --> 32:23.984
YOU KNOW THE DEAL.
YOU GOT FIVE MINUTES TO LOOK.

32:23.984 --> 32:26.028
IT'S THREE BEDROOMS,
SOME DEN THING.

32:26.028 --> 32:27.905
IT'S A 60615 ZIP CODE.

32:27.905 --> 32:29.406
IT'S GOOD SHIT.

32:29.406 --> 32:31.742
- HOW MUCH
FOR THE BARCALOUNGERS?

32:31.742 --> 32:33.035
- I GOT TO DO THIS
WITH YOU AGAIN?

32:33.035 --> 32:34.953
IT'S NOT A FUCKING
ANTIQUE ROAD SHOW.

32:34.953 --> 32:36.663
YOU BID ON THE WHOLE THING
OR NOTHING AT ALL.

32:36.663 --> 32:38.165
- SHIT.

32:38.165 --> 32:39.958
I LIKE BARCALOUNGERS.

32:39.958 --> 32:42.003
- GREAT, BUY THE TRUCK
AND GET YOUR BARCALOUNGERS.

32:42.003 --> 32:43.504
THINK I'M GONNA STAND
AROUND HERE SELLING EACH PIECE

32:43.504 --> 32:45.506
FOR 5 BUCKS
LIKE IT'S A FUCKING YARD SALE?

32:45.506 --> 32:47.008
- GIVE YOU 4 GRAND
FOR THE LOT.

32:47.008 --> 32:49.093
- 4.
- I'LL GIVE YOU $4,500.

32:49.093 --> 32:52.012
- ANYONE ELSE?
- 5 GRAND.

32:52.012 --> 32:54.598
- $5,300.
I WANT THOSE BARCALOUNGERS.

32:54.598 --> 32:57.434
- YEAH, WE KNOW.
- NAH, I'M OUT.

32:57.434 --> 32:59.436
- YEAH, ME TOO.

32:59.436 --> 33:02.314
- SOLD TO THE MAN
WITH THE BARCALOUNGER FETISH.

33:07.569 --> 33:09.072
- IT'S ALL THERE?
- IT'S THERE.

33:09.072 --> 33:10.406
- ALL RIGHT.

33:19.331 --> 33:20.833
- NEED A RIDE?

33:23.419 --> 33:24.878
- YOU'RE LATE.

33:24.878 --> 33:26.255
- GROCERY STORE WAS BUSY.

33:33.429 --> 33:36.014
- COME ON, V,
FREE POUR LIKE KEV DOES.

33:36.014 --> 33:38.058
- THAT'S WHY
THE BAR'S LOSING MONEY.

33:42.980 --> 33:45.233
- YUM, IT TASTES JUST LIKE
TONIC WATER.

33:47.359 --> 33:48.527
- LIP.

33:48.527 --> 33:49.987
- HEY, V.

33:49.987 --> 33:52.114
HEY, TOMMY.
- HEY, LIP.

33:52.114 --> 33:54.158
- SAMMI.

33:54.158 --> 33:56.452
- WHEN DID SAMMI START
HANGING OUT AT THE ALIBI?

33:56.452 --> 33:59.079
- THAT GIRL IS HORNIER THAN
A THREE-PECKERED BILLY GOAT.

33:59.079 --> 34:01.249
- [giggling]
STOP IT.

34:01.249 --> 34:02.875
- SO WHAT BRINGS YOU HERE,
COLLEGE BOY?

34:02.875 --> 34:04.543
- WELL, I CAME TO GET
THE DETAILS ABOUT THE JOB.

34:04.543 --> 34:06.837
- YEAH, WHAT JOB'S THAT?
HEY, GET COLLEGE A BEER HERE,

34:06.837 --> 34:08.214
WILL YOU, V?
- DEMO'ING.

34:08.214 --> 34:09.423
ARE YOU STILL DOING THAT?
- YEP.

34:09.423 --> 34:11.217
ABOUT TO START
A BIG CLEANUP.

34:11.217 --> 34:13.510
THEY KNOCKED OVER SUNNY DAYS
ON HALSTED THIS MORNING.

34:13.510 --> 34:14.928
- GREAT. I'M IN.

34:14.928 --> 34:16.847
- LIKE HELL YOU ARE.

34:16.847 --> 34:18.141
- WELL,
YOU PROMISED ME A JOB.

34:18.141 --> 34:19.725
- YEAH?
HOW DRUNK WAS I?

34:19.725 --> 34:22.644
- I--I NEED THE MONEY
FOR SCHOOL, OKAY?

34:22.644 --> 34:24.730
- I DON'T HIRE COLLEGE PUSSIES
LIKE YOU.

34:24.730 --> 34:26.106
TRY THE GAP ON MICHIGAN.

34:26.106 --> 34:27.858
- TOO LATE IN THE SUMMER
TO GET ANOTHER JOB.

34:27.858 --> 34:29.818
WE HAD A DEAL.

34:29.818 --> 34:31.862
- YOU'RE AN IDIOT.
I'M JUST BUSTING YOUR BALLS.

34:31.862 --> 34:33.405
- FUCK YOU.

34:33.405 --> 34:35.157
- FIRST DAY OF WORK
YOU'LL BE CRYING LIKE A BABY,

34:35.157 --> 34:37.326
BEGGING TO GO HOME BY LUNCH.
- YEAH, WE'LL SEE.

34:37.326 --> 34:39.870
- HEY, BE SURE TO WRITE
YOUR BLOOD TYPE ON YOUR BOOTS

34:39.870 --> 34:41.288
FOR WHEN YOU SEVER A LIMB.

34:41.288 --> 34:43.124
- OH, BOOTS?
I WAS GONNA WEAR FLIP-FLOPS.

34:43.124 --> 34:44.458
- [laughing]

34:44.458 --> 34:47.336
I'M GONNA ENJOY FUCKING
WITH YOU ALL SUMMER.

34:47.336 --> 34:48.462
- WELCOME HOME, LIP.

34:48.462 --> 34:50.214
- THANKS, V.

34:50.214 --> 34:52.007
- [sarcastically]
"FLIP-FLOPS."

34:52.007 --> 34:53.800
- HOW DO YOU NOT HAVE
ANY TATTOOS?

34:53.800 --> 34:55.719
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU
FOR A SECOND.

34:55.719 --> 34:57.221
- WELL, IT'S TRUE.

34:57.221 --> 35:01.475
MAYBE I'LL LET YOU DO
A FULL BODY SCAN SOMETIME.

35:01.475 --> 35:03.101
- COME SEE OUR SHOW
TONIGHT, HUH?

35:03.101 --> 35:05.854
- NO, I WISH I COULD.
I TURN INTO A PUMPKIN AT 9:00.

35:05.854 --> 35:08.398
- WHAT IF I
COME BY AFTER MY GIG?

35:11.818 --> 35:13.737
YOU TEXT ME...

35:13.737 --> 35:16.532
IF YOU'RE FEELING RANDY.

35:16.532 --> 35:17.908
- OKAY.

35:17.908 --> 35:20.786
[funk music]

35:20.786 --> 35:28.877
♪ ♪

35:33.465 --> 35:36.302
- GIRL,
DAVIS IS ALL OVER YOU.

35:36.302 --> 35:39.305
- DUDE IS FIRE,
AND THAT ACCENT?

35:39.305 --> 35:42.225
UGH, FALLS IN THE BAD CHOICE
CATEGORY.

35:42.225 --> 35:44.434
I SHOULD KNOW.

35:44.434 --> 35:46.061
GOD, YOU SCARED ME.

35:46.061 --> 35:48.480
- THAT'S FOR YOU.
- THANKS, FIONA.

35:48.480 --> 35:49.690
- YEAH, SEE YOU, FIONA.

35:49.690 --> 35:51.149
- BYE, GUYS.
- TAKE CARE.

35:51.149 --> 35:54.611
- MAYBE I'LL SEE YOU LATER,
HUH?

35:54.611 --> 35:55.988
- MM.

35:55.988 --> 35:58.324
both: "MAYBE I'LL SEE
YOU LATER."

35:59.908 --> 36:01.244
- DID HE LEAVE
A GOOD TIP?

36:01.244 --> 36:02.619
- WAIT, HE ONLY
GAVE YOU THE TIP?

36:02.619 --> 36:04.621
HE DIDN'T STICK
THE WHOLE THING IN?

36:04.621 --> 36:06.081
- BE CAREFUL.
HE'S A MUSICIAN.

36:06.081 --> 36:08.125
YOU NEVER KNOW WHERE
THAT TIP'S BEEN.

36:08.125 --> 36:10.669
- AW, ARE YOU JEALOUS, SEAN?
- WHO'S COMING WITH ME?

36:10.669 --> 36:12.629
I'M HEADING OUT TO THE MEETING.
- YEAH, I'M COMING.

36:12.629 --> 36:13.839
- NO, I CAN'T.
WORKING DOUBLE.

36:13.839 --> 36:15.299
- FIONA?

36:15.299 --> 36:18.176
- UH, NAH, FAMILY'S COMING
IN FOR EARLY DINNER.

36:18.176 --> 36:20.012
I'M GONNA STICK AROUND
AND WAIT ON THEM.

36:20.012 --> 36:22.389
- WELL, I'LL BE BACK LATER
TO SAY HI AND MEET LIP.

36:22.389 --> 36:24.016
- OKAY, GREAT.

36:28.396 --> 36:29.896
- HEY.

36:29.896 --> 36:31.773
- WHY'D YOU WANT
TO MEET HERE?

36:31.773 --> 36:33.275
- GET ME SOME
OF THOSE WOOD CHIPS.

36:33.275 --> 36:35.193
WOULD YOU?
PUT THEM IN HERE.

36:35.193 --> 36:37.112
- FOR YOUR WORK PROJECT?

36:37.112 --> 36:39.573
- YEAH.

36:39.573 --> 36:41.283
- WHY CAN'T YOU
DO THIS YOURSELF?

36:41.283 --> 36:43.869
- A GROWN MAN
DIGGING AT THE FEET OF KIDS

36:43.869 --> 36:45.787
LOOKS A LITTLE PERVY,
DON'T YOU THINK?

36:45.787 --> 36:48.374
- THIS IS GONNA COST
YOU MORE MONEY.

36:48.374 --> 36:50.584
- WHAT YOU GOT?

36:50.584 --> 36:52.377
THAT'S GOOD.

36:52.377 --> 36:53.754
COME ON.

36:53.754 --> 36:56.006
WE'RE GONNA BE LATE
FOR DINNER.

36:58.800 --> 37:00.927
- THANK YOU.

37:00.927 --> 37:03.305
OKAY, SEE, CHUCKIE,

37:03.305 --> 37:06.350
IT'S NOT THAT I DON'T
WANT YOU AT MY HOUSE ANYMORE,

37:06.350 --> 37:09.978
OR YOUR MOM, IT'S JUST THAT--
LOOK, THIS IS WHERE YOU BELONG.

37:09.978 --> 37:11.438
THIS IS YOUR HOUSE,

37:11.438 --> 37:13.273
AND YOU'RE WELCOME TO COME
AND VISIT SOMETIMES,

37:13.273 --> 37:15.734
BUT YOU HAVE
TO CALL FIRST, OKAY?

