- AND?

50:49.672 --> 50:52.091
- JACKASS IS A BETTER MOM
THAN ME.

50:52.091 --> 50:54.051
[phone chimes]

51:02.268 --> 51:05.272
WHO'S THAT?

51:05.272 --> 51:07.149
- NOBODY.

51:07.149 --> 51:08.858
YOU KNOW WHAT WE SHOULD DO?

51:08.858 --> 51:10.234
POOL PARTY!

51:10.234 --> 51:11.235
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

51:11.235 --> 51:12.820
- GO TELL YOUR BROTHERS.

51:12.820 --> 51:15.156
