- ALL RIGHT, CARL, GET HIM!

52:39.366 --> 52:41.826
- I'VE GOT A DAY
FULL OF RAGE INSIDE OF ME.

52:41.826 --> 52:44.120
- GET HER NOW!
- TAKE HIM DOWN.

52:44.120 --> 52:47.290
- GO GET HIM, DEBS, GET HIM!
- ALL YOU ALL MUST DIE!

52:47.290 --> 52:48.332
- [screaming]

52:48.332 --> 52:50.626
- OH, YEAH.
- [laughing]

52:50.626 --> 52:53.254
- OH, HEY, NOW.
- YOU GUYS ARE CHEATERS.

52:53.254 --> 52:55.047
- LOOK WHO'S A SORE SPORT.

52:55.047 --> 52:56.632
- LOOK WHO'S MADLY IN LOVE.

52:56.632 --> 52:58.218
- YOU GOT ROOM FOR ONE MORE?

52:58.218 --> 52:59.719
all: IAN!

52:59.719 --> 53:02.471
- I GOT YOUR TEXT.
- WHERE'S MICKEY?

53:02.471 --> 53:04.307
- I WORE HIM OUT.

53:04.307 --> 53:06.226
- ALL RIGHT, COME ON,
IT'S OUR TURN IN THE POOL.

53:06.226 --> 53:09.229
LET'S GO, WILL. ARE YOU READY?
- GO, LIAM, GO.

53:09.229 --> 53:10.397
- OKAY, WILL.

53:10.397 --> 53:15.318
- COME ON.
- LIAM.

53:15.318 --> 53:17.153
- ALL RIGHT, LIAM,
YOU'RE GOING DOWN.

53:17.153 --> 53:18.654
- HEY, SHUT UP DOWN THERE!

53:18.654 --> 53:19.822
- OH, YOU SHUT UP!
IT'S SUMMER!

